data.description: On top of the world with panoramic city lights views. Beautiful Blanca model with 2 bedrooms, 2 baths, and attached garage. Approximately 1100 square feet of beauty. Freshly painted on the interior. Lush new carpet throughout. Remodeled guest bathroom. Large living room with cozy fireplace. Bright kitchen with panoramic views. Large patio with forever views. A beautiful place to call home. Community is spread throughout 484 acres with mature trees & beautiful hills. Association offers two recreation center which offers pool, spa, club house, tennis, gym, paddle tennis, shuffleboard courts, billiards & much more. Trash pickup & outside painting are covered by the association. This is a 55+. Member of Lake Mission with picnic, swimming, fishing, sport courts and much more.
